    <p>That day actually comes in closer to 140g — which is fine. Hitting 130g as a floor means some days you'll land at 135g or 140g. That's the right direction. The target is a floor, not a ceiling.</p>

    <h2>The Difference Between 120g and 130g in Practice</h2>

    <p>Most men who are hitting 120g consistently find that 130g requires exactly one change. Not a new meal, not a restructured diet — just one deliberate addition somewhere in the day.</p>

